    • EvtChannelConfigEnabled

      static final int EvtChannelConfigEnabled
      Identifies the enabled attribute of the channel. The variant type for this property is EvtVarTypeBoolean. You cannot set this property for the Application, System, and Security channels.
      See Also:
      • Constant Field Values

    • EvtChannelConfigIsolation

      static final int EvtChannelConfigIsolation
      Identifies the isolation attribute of the channel. The variant type for this property is EvtVarTypeUInt32. For possible isolation values, see the Winevt.EVT_CHANNEL_ISOLATION_TYPE enumeration. You cannot set this property for the Application, System, and Security channels.
      See Also:

      static final int EvtChannelConfigType
